The '''''Phalanx''''' was a [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] [[Cruiser/Legends|cruiser]] that was severely damaged at the [[Battle of Doornik-319]]. When the ''Phalanx'' tried to tractor in a crippled [[BTL-S8 K-wing assault starfighter|K-wing]] it was fired on, destroying the K-wing and damaging the ''Phalanx''.

